### REFRESH ACCESS TOKEN
# @name refresh
POST http://localhost:8080/api/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshToken}}

@accessToken = {{refresh.response.body.$.token}}

### LIST CHIRPS OF AUTHOR
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chirps
  ?author_id={{userId}}
  &sort=asc

